name: Air France 777-228ER [F-GSPE] Landing at Vancouver Airport ᴴᴰ
description:
Air France started flights to Vancouver in March 2015, serving the route 3 times a week in the winter and 5 times in the summer. Here we have one of AF's many 772s arriving on runway 26R in May 2016, with ATC included! Enjoy.

Thanks for watching!
